race.comment: TIGGERLONG BINGO (1) is better than last start when fifth (19.06) in a NG at Temora over 330m. Has a good record here at this journey. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. WESTSIDE BLISS (7) missed the frame last time out when seventh at Temora from Box three (19.23) but draws same box here as latest win. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. One of the main contenders. LUCY VALENTINE (8) last raced on July 30 when fourth (19.93) over 340m at Gunnedah in a Free For All. Overall form off this box is sound. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. MALA ANGEL (2) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.
